(806, 1, '2017-03-20 07:17:22', '2017-03-20 07:17:22', '[vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1502176739662{margin-top: 27px !important;margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\" el_class=\"faq\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_toggle title=\"What is Delight Pet Shop?\" css=\".vc_custom_1539608072476{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\"]Delight Pet Shop is a pet boarding/sitting, and pet care solution provider. We help pet lovers and pet owners connect. Pet owners travelling can find a suitable sitter for their pet, while they are away. All you have to do is, choose a reliable and Delight pet Shop verified sitter through our portal, make reservations, pay online, and leave your pet at the sitters care on the decided date!\r\n\r\n[/vc_toggle][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1498209422486{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\" el_class=\"faq\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_toggle title=\"How Delight Pet Shop works?\" css=\".vc_custom_1539608147475{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\"]Delight Pet Shop currently only operates in Pune and has plans of expanding to other cities. Pet owners choose a suitable sitter for boarding their pet through our online portal while they are away. Owners screen experienced sitters who are registered with us, based on their profile, reviews and pricing, make reservations, pay online and leave their pet at the sitter on the decided date.\r\n[/vc_toggle][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1498209434459{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\" el_class=\"faq\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_toggle title=\"How do I pay for Delight Pet Shop services?\" css=\".vc_custom_1539608235395{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\"]You can pay for Delight Pet Shop from the comforts of your home online using your credit /debit card, net banking.\r\n[/vc_toggle][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"faq\" css=\".vc_custom_1502176705286{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_toggle title=\"Whom should I contact in case of an emergency for the pet?\" css=\".vc_custom_1539608411571{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\"]In case of any emergency like illness, accident or any other dire situations pertaining to the well being of the pet, sitters are advised to contact the pet owners first, informing them about the situation. In case the owner is not in a position to come down and collect the pet immediately, both sitters and pet owners can contact +919823090884.[/vc_toggle][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'FAQ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'faq', '', '', '2018-10-15 13:09:33', '2018-10-15 13:09:33', '', 0, 'https://demo.themeftc.com/woo-peto/store///?page_id=806', 0, 'page', '', 0),
